6 (20) Usable cannabis. – The dried buds and mature female flowers of the plant of
7 the genus Cannabis, and any mixture or preparation thereof, that are
8 appropriate for medical use as provided in this Article.
9 (21) Vaping. – The use of a product which heats a liquid or other form of cannabis
