1 (3) In a vehicle.
2 (4) In or within 1,000 linear feet of the property line of a church, unless the
3 medical use occurs within a private residence.
4 (5) In or within 1,000 linear feet of the property line of a child care facility as
5 defined in G.S. 110-86(3), unless the medical use occurs within a private
6 residence. When a private residence is a child care facility, the smoking of
7 cannabis and the vaping of cannabis is prohibited.
